data.description: Stunning curb appeal, oversized great room, and prime location, this home has it all! Located in highly sought after NISD, this stunning home boasts an open floor plan that seamlessly connects the kitchen, living room, and breakfast nook, making it perfect for entertaining guests or social gatherings. The high soaring ceilings allow for plenty of natural light to flood the space, creating a bright and welcoming ambiance. Upstairs, you'll find a flexible living space that can be used as a home office, media room, or even a playroom. The primary bedroom is conveniently located on the main level, offering a peaceful retreat. Outside you will find a spacious yard that is easily turned into your own backyard oasis! Community includes a pool, sports court, and clubhouse! Convenient location to major highways, shopping, and a number of restaurants! Schedule a showing today to be one step closer to making this your next dream home!
